author: Kevin Freking, Associated Press
title: Obama urges supporters to stay engaged, says he will too
text: Photo: Pablo Martinez Monsivais, AP Basketball player Stephen Curry, center, with his teammates from the Golden State Warriors on stage with the 2015 NBA championship trophy during a Democratic fundraiser at the Warfield Theater, Saturday, Oct. 10, 2015 in San Francisco. Basketball player Stephen Curry, center, with his teammates from... SAN FRANCISCO (AP) — President Barack Obama on Saturday encouraged supporters to be politically active, saying that he plans to remain so when his presidency concludes and declared, "I'm just getting started."
